  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >LEMURIA is a third-person shooter with action elements, set against the backdrop of street riots and the outbreak of a deadly epidemic. Players will take on the roles of two protagonists — veteran Alex Rain and adventurer Kanta Anora — whose fates intertwine through a series of unexpected events.  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/917940/extras/3d6a7c9aeeb0e0d5de282c09158344a7.avif?t=1735889221\" width=615 height=308 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Protagonists</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Alex</strong>, trying to cope with the shadows of his past, faces not only real dangers but also projections of his own fears. His post-traumatic stress disorder (PTSD) causes him to question the reality of events; every new situation triggers memories of forgotten horrors, making him believe he is back on the battlefield — and he throws himself into that fight. Alex avoids old friends, invents imaginary romances with women he randomly encounters, and tries to impose his truth on everyone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Kanta</strong>, on the other hand, creates chaos around her even in the simplest situations. She has a restless spark, a tendency toward nymphomania, and constantly seeks thrills. Every interaction she has is a game where the rules exist only to allow her to test boundaries. Even the most innocent tasks can spark a real storm, and her unbridled thirst for adventure often puts everything at risk.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Intense firefights with the option to choose between direct confrontation or careful progression.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dialogue-based cutscenes that reveal the characters' personalities and drive the narrative forward.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An uncompromising atmosphere inspired by 80s VHS action movies, complemented by adult content elements.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customizable gameplay, allowing players to tailor the experience to their preferences.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Diverse game locations: the nightmare of a medical quarantine; the chaos of the streets in an ethnic enclave; the scorching heat of the Middle East; the labyrinths of the villains’ hideout; the deceptive safety of wealthy suburbs; a forest road motel turned massacre site; and the illusory world of fantasies.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The 2.0 update reintroduced previously cut scenes, a new full voiceover, and numerous improvements.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Conclusion</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >LEMURIA offers a refined experience for several evenings, where players will face moral dilemmas and immerse themselves in a tense world where every step could be their last. This is the first part of an exciting adventure series.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/917940/extras/99085cc1fe93ed948222adb364cddaec.avif?t=1735889221\" width=615 height=250 /></span></p>",
